App                     RDesk Application
async                   Wrap a message handler to run asynchronously
                        with zero configuration
build_app               Build a self-contained distributable from an
                        RDesk application
rdesk_async             Run a task in the background
rdesk_cancel_job        Cancel a running background job
rdesk_create_app        Create a new RDesk application project
rdesk_is_bundle         Check if the app is running in a bundled
                        (standalone) environment
rdesk_jobs_pending      Check if any background jobs are pending
rdesk_service           Service all active RDesk applications
